    "asOf": "2020-11-12",
    "date": "2020-12-11T22:09:56Z",
    "text": "Rohingya Genocide Determination Act of 2020\n\nThis bill requires the Department of State to report to Congress an assessment of the persecution of the Rohingya, a predominantly Muslim group in Burma (Myanmar), by Burma's military and security forces, and whether the situation constitutes genocide under U.S. law."
